  "description": "Yesterday I babbled rather philosophically about how to determine how determined something is by how many absurd statements can be said to make it necessary, which is affirmed by how many absurdities require those necessities to be possible.\nAnd then in the evening I started looking at if there was a tool I\u0026rsquo;d like better than Quartz for publishing my site, because with the amount of data I\u0026rsquo;m working with, Quartz was not working out; build times were pushing toward 5-10 minutes.\n",
